+ *             this protocol won't be in the list unless compiled in, so
+ *             the average user (w/out VLANs) will not be adversely affected.
+ *             --BLG
+ *
+ *		0800	IP
+ *		8100    802.1Q VLAN
+ *		0001	802.3
+ *		0002	AX.25
+ *		0004	802.2
+ *		8035	RARP
+ *		0005	SNAP
+ *		0805	X.25
+ *		0806	ARP
+ *		8137	IPX
+ *		0009	Localtalk
+ *		86DD	IPv6
+ */
